---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { locales } from '../data/locales';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Free Online Screen"
  description="Read the privacy policy for Free Online Screen. We are committed to a serverless, tracker-free experience that respects your privacy."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
  lang={locales.en.lang}
  locale="en"
>
  <section class="site-shell py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Data Protection</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl font-semibold leading-[0.95] text-balance text-ink md:text-6xl">Privacy Policy.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-body text-balance">
        Your privacy is our priority. Free Online Screen does not collect, record, track, or share your personal information.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-hairline bg-canvas">
    <article class="rich-article site-shell max-w-3xl py-12 md:py-16">
      <h2>No Personal Data Collection</h2>
      <p>
        Free Online Screen operates as a static client-side web utility. We do not require registration, accounts, email signups, or logins. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data, search histories, IP lists, or usage statistics to our servers.
      </p>

      <h2>Local Browser Storage</h2>
      <p>
        We use standard browser features like local storage solely to preserve your configuration choices. This includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Your preference for Dark Mode or Light Mode theme selection.</li>
        <li>Custom colors, speeds, styles, or configuration choices chosen in the screensavers and prank tools.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This data is stored purely on your local device and is never uploaded anywhere. You can clear this data at any time by clearing your browser cache or site data.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies & Third-Party Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We do not use advertising cookies, marketing pixels, or tracking tools (like Google Analytics). Your activities on our platform remain completely anonymous and local to your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting & Logs</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is hosted on static deployment platforms. The servers hosting this application automatically log standard HTTP requests (such as your User-Agent and generalized IP address range) to prevent distributed denial-of-service (DDoS) requests and ensure infrastructure security. These system logs are managed by our hosting provider and are periodically purged.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect modifications in our software. Since no email or demographic identities are collected, we recommend checking this page to stay informed of updates.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or feedback regarding our privacy practices, feel free to contact us through our <a class="text-link hover:underline" href="/contact/">Contact Page</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
